Your newborn’s photo fills the front and is overlayed with "she’s here!" "he’s here!" or "I’am here!" in a contemporary script (you can move this text to another area on the card depending on your photo by selecting "edit in design tool"). Add his or her name, arrival date and birth stats. On the reverse side, add four additional family photos, a "welcomed by" message and the parent’s and siblings first names. Price:$2.39
